Package com.poesys.ms.pk

Interface Summary
IPrimaryKey A generic interface for primary key data transfer objects.
 

Class Summary
AbstractPrimaryKey An abstract implementation of the IPrimaryKey interface that implements elements shared between all the primary key classes.
AssociationPrimaryKey A concrete implementation of the IPrimaryKey interface that represents an association primary key.
CompositePrimaryKey An implementation of the IPrimaryKey interface that represents a composite primary key.
GuidPrimaryKey Implements the IPrimaryKey interface for a key constructed from a single UUID value.
IdentityPrimaryKey Implements the identity primary key (a generated integer value key).
NaturalPrimaryKey Implements the IPrimaryKey interface with a list of single-valued columns.
SequencePrimaryKey Implements the sequence primary key (a generated integer value)
